channel.title: Fantom '87 & Zeph - Wave Racer (E/E's Club Mix) [House, Synthwave]
channel.description:
https://soundcloud.com/eslashe/zeph-fantom-87-wave-racer-eslashe-remix
Remix for the remix contest currently being held on the [Auxy Discord for this song currently](https://discord.gg/7yguA4S). I was so excited to get to be able to remix this track, it's so amazing and I loved it the second it was even discussed. Amazing job @Zeph and @Fantom87 for such a fantastic song.
